book.rituals.base.knowledge.1=This ritual will let you dive into the world of the Eldritch. It will add other rituals and more knowledge to this book. The only thing need to perform this easy ritual (besides the simbols) is this book.
book.rituals.base.knowledge.2=Be warned that venturing too far into the world of the eldritch can be detremental to one's own health. You have been warned.
book.rituals.base.knowledge.success=You feel yourself becoming, just slightly, more versed.
#Sunny:
book.rituals.one.sunny=The Sun Call
book.rituals.one.sunny.1=Let the sun be yours to call; but not yours to command, not yet. This ritual will clear away rain and make the sun rise up into the heavens.
book.rituals.one.sunny.2=An extra thing needed for this ritual is a bottle of blood, the controller of the sun does need to be feed now and again.
book.rituals.one.sunny.success=The sun controller heeds your request, and decides to comply.

